NK122(kho)001:1: // dam pa bde gshegs kyis mdzad pa'i theg dgu spyi
NK122(kho)001:2: chings kyi rtsa ba gsung rab rin po che'i mdzod
NK122(kho)001:4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)001:5: mnyam nyid chos sku gsang ba'i sku //
NK122(kho)001:6: longs spyod rdzogs sku sprul pa'i sku //
NK122(kho)001:7: sku lnga'i bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das //
NK122(kho)001:8: dpal ldan kun bzang phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)001:10: shes ldan kun la phan gdags phyir //
NK122(kho)001:11: tshad ma gsum dang mi 'gal bar //
NK122(kho)001:12: theg pa kun gyi spyi chings brjod //
NK122(kho)001:13: chos rnams kun gyi gnas tshul ni //
NK122(kho)001:14: ldog phyogs rnam pa lnga ru 'gyur //
NK122(kho)001:15: gnas tshul 'khrul dang thugs rjes gzigs //
NK122(kho)001:16: thugs rje skyes nas don mdzad tshul //
NK122(kho)001:17: mtshon tshul brjod pa rim bstan kyang //
NK122(kho)001:18: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs kyis //
NK122(kho)001:19: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pas na //
NK122(kho)001:20: snga phyi med par mnyam rdzogs yin //
NK122(kho)001:21: thog mar bstan pa'i don nyid ni //
NK122(kho)001:22: dkyil 'khor gsum po dbyer med cing //
NK122(kho)001:23: shes bya kun gyi gzhir gnas pas //
NK122(kho)001:24: thams cad ngo bo mnyam pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:25: lhan cig byed dang nye bar len //
NK122(kho)001:26: ma rig rnam pa gnyis mthu yis //
NK122(kho)001:27: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtog /
NK122(kho)001:28: rgyal po'i phru gu 'khyams pa bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:29: gsum gnyis bzhi yi rkyen dag gis //
NK122(kho)001:30: bskyed dang phan dang stobs rgyas byed //
NK122(kho)001:32: zhen mthus rmi lam brtas pa bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:33: ye nas bde gshegs snying po las //
NK122(kho)001:34: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK122(kho)001:35: bde sdug yul dus lus la sogs //
NK122(kho)001:36: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK122(kho)001:38: srid pa ming tsam log pa'i stobs //
NK122(kho)001:39: de bas ting 'dzin mnyam dang bral //
NK122(kho)001:40: de la tha tshig phyi dang nang //
NK122(kho)001:41: rang bzhin phung po khams bzhin gnas //
NK122(kho)001:42: skye rgas na dang 'chi ba dang //
NK122(kho)001:43: 'jig chags stong gnas bzhi po ni //
NK122(kho)001:44: rten 'brel bcu gnyis tshul dag tu //
NK122(kho)001:46: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK122(kho)001:47: gdul byar gzigs par mdzad pa yang //
NK122(kho)001:48: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pas na //
NK122(kho)001:49: rnam rtog mi mnga' sa ler mkhyen //
NK122(kho)001:50: log par rtog brtags rnam dag cing //
NK122(kho)001:51: de bzhin nyid las mi gzhan phyir //
NK122(kho)001:52: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pas na //
NK122(kho)001:53: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK122(kho)001:54: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos te //
NK122(kho)001:55: chos kyi dbyings su dbyer med kyang //
NK122(kho)001:56: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rig pa nyid //
NK122(kho)001:57: ye shes yul bral dus gcig 'char //
NK122(kho)001:58: thugs rje chen po'i byung tshul ni //
NK122(kho)001:59: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs skye dang //
NK122(kho)001:60: yul dang phrad nas skye ba dang //
NK122(kho)001:61: bskul zhing gsol btab tshul gyis skye //
NK122(kho)001:62: nam mkha' lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK122(kho)001:63: 'byung bzhi lta bu'i gdul bya la //
NK122(kho)001:64: bya btsal med par brdal khyab pa'ang //
NK122(kho)001:65: mtha' dbus dbri bkol rgyun chad med //
NK122(kho)001:66: 'gro drug gdul bya thams cad la //
NK122(kho)001:67: 'byung chen yongs snyoms thugs rje yis //
NK122(kho)001:68: bskyed 'tsho brten sogs bya ba rnams //
NK122(kho)001:69: spang len med par rgyun du 'char //
NK122(kho)001:70: nyi ma lta bu'i thugs rje yis //
NK122(kho)001:71: gling bzhir gnas pa'i snang ba kun //
NK122(kho)001:72: dbri bkol med par khyab pa bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:73: spang len med pa'i thugs rje 'char //
NK122(kho)001:75: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK122(kho)001:76: zla rgyas lta bu spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK122(kho)001:77: thugs rje nyi shar bzhin du snyoms mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)001:78: zhes gsungs lung gis bgrod dang sla //
NK122(kho)001:81: gdul bya'i khams rnams ma lus par //
NK122(kho)001:82: dag dang ma dag grags ma grags //
NK122(kho)001:83: sprul pa'i 'khor lo rgyun mi chad //
NK122(kho)001:84: lung las kyang ni 'di skad gsungs //
NK122(kho)001:85: sprul pa ni ma byung ma myong rgyun du 'byung ba'o //
NK122(kho)001:86: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ni de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos par /
NK122(kho)001:87: sems can gyi khams 'du shes mtha' thug pa med pa dang gzugs dang /
NK122(kho)001:89: spyod pa mtha' thug pa med pa rnams /
NK122(kho)001:93: mi 'grel ba ni gang yang med do //
NK122(kho)001:94: de skad gsungs dgongs pa 'dus pa'i lung las kun
NK122(kho)001:95: bzang gis pas kun mkhyen gyis yang dag rdzogs pa'i
NK122(kho)001:96: sangs rgyas // gdul byar gyur pa yul la sprul pa rgyun chad med par 'byung ste /
NK122(kho)001:97: gtan tshigs ci'i phyir byung na thams cad kun //
NK122(kho)001:98: rang bzhin dbye ba med pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:99: zhen gnyis dag dang thugs rje'i phyir //
NK122(kho)001:100: zhen pa mi mnga' sa ler mkhyen //
NK122(kho)001:101: rang bzhin shugs kyis skye ba ni //
NK122(kho)001:102: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad ni //
NK122(kho)001:103: zhen pa gnyis kyi mun pa dngas //
NK122(kho)001:104: 'gro drug mun pa gnyis kyis bsgribs //
NK122(kho)001:105: gnyid sad pa yi skyes bu'i drung //
NK122(kho)001:106: gnyid kyis non pa ji lta bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:107: dam pa rnams kyi thugs rje yis //
NK122(kho)001:108: mi gzigs mi mkhyen gang yang med //
NK122(kho)001:109: yul dang phrad pa'i thugs rje ni //
NK122(kho)001:110: sngon byung thar pa nag po sogs //
NK122(kho)001:111: khyad par las kyis sbyangs pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:112: rdo rje theg la brten log ste //
NK122(kho)001:113: gol sa rnams su song ba dag /
NK122(kho)001:114: bdag gzhan kun la gnod pa las //
NK122(kho)001:115: kun mkhyen thugs rjes yongs gzigs nas //
NK122(kho)001:116: zhi ba'i dbyings las ma g.yos par //
NK122(kho)001:117: 'bar ba chen po'i cha lugs kyis //
NK122(kho)001:118: 'khor bcas dug gsum gnas su sbyong //
NK122(kho)001:119: rnam shes zag med dbyings su bsgral //
NK122(kho)001:120: dper na sbyin bdag phyug po yis //
NK122(kho)001:121: long sprang mthong bar gyur pa'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:122: snying rje'i zas kyis tshim byas pas //
NK122(kho)001:123: bkren pa'i sdug bsngal bsal bzhin no //
NK122(kho)001:124: bskul zhing gsol ba gdab pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:125: ston pa mya ngan 'das rjes nas //
NK122(kho)001:126: brgya dang bcu gnyis lo yi dus //
NK122(kho)001:127: dri med grags sogs dam pa rnams //
NK122(kho)001:128: ma la ya yi rtse la lhags //
NK122(kho)001:129: bdag gzhan kun gyis don gyi phyir //
NK122(kho)001:130: gdung tshigs nyi shu rtsa gsum gyis //
NK122(kho)001:131: phyogs bcu'i rgyal la gsol ba gdab //
NK122(kho)001:132: rgyal ba'i thugs rjes de dgongs nas //
NK122(kho)001:133: sprul pa gsang bdag gnas su 'dus //
NK122(kho)001:134: lung chen tshig gis bgro bar byas //
NK122(kho)001:135: gsang bdag rgyal tshab chen po yis //
NK122(kho)001:136: gdung ba bsal bar zhal gyis bzhes //
NK122(kho)001:137: ma la ya yi rtse la byon //
NK122(kho)001:138: rdo rje theg pa char bzhin phab //
NK122(kho)001:139: ri rab rtse dang u rgyan gnas //
NK122(kho)001:140: lha min dbang po'i khang bzang dang //
NK122(kho)001:141: gnod sbyin rgyal po'i pho brang dang //
NK122(kho)001:142: mkha' 'gro pho mo'i gnas rnams su //
NK122(kho)001:143: gdul bya so so'i mos pa bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:144: bstan pa'i snying po gsang sngags bshad //
NK122(kho)001:145: rdo rje theg pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK122(kho)001:146: rgyal po dza sogs skal ldan rnams //
NK122(kho)001:147: tshe gcig rdzogs sangs rgyas gyur te //
NK122(kho)001:148: 'khor bcas zhi ba chen por gshegs //
NK122(kho)001:149: slad nas 'gro ba skal ldan gyis //
NK122(kho)001:150: sgrub pa rtse gcig mos pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:151: rang rang lha la gsol btab pas //
NK122(kho)001:152: bsnyen sgrub yan lag gzhung bzhin spyad //
NK122(kho)001:153: lta spyod dam tshig ma nor te //
NK122(kho)001:154: bsam gtan brtson ldan mthar phyin pas //
NK122(kho)001:155: las dang nyon mongs dag gyur te //
NK122(kho)001:156: 'dod pa lha yi zhal gzigs shing //
NK122(kho)001:157: lung bstan 'bras bu mngon du byas //
NK122(kho)001:158: de dag thugs rje bskul ba dang //
NK122(kho)001:159: dag thob gsol ba btab pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:160: thugs rje yin pa rgyal bas gsungs //
NK122(kho)001:161: thugs rje skyes nas don mdzad tshul //
NK122(kho)001:162: rnam pa gsum du shes bya ste //
NK122(kho)001:163: gdul bya 'dul thabs theg pa yang //
NK122(kho)001:164: re re'ang gsum du gnas pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:166: gdul dka' drag po'i gdul bya rnams //
NK122(kho)001:167: 'khor lo rgyun dang don dam nges //
NK122(kho)001:169: rang bzhin shugs dang gnyen po'i thabs //
NK122(kho)001:170: las ngan las rgyun gcod pa gsum //
NK122(kho)001:171: gdul bya theg pa 'dul thabs su //
NK122(kho)001:172: mdor bsdus nas ni bstan pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:173: de dag rgyas par bshad pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:174: 'khor lo rgyun gyi gdul bya ni /
NK122(kho)001:175: khams gsum gnas pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK122(kho)001:176: zhen gsum 'dod pa ma bral bas //
NK122(kho)001:177: 'dod la zhen pa'i gdul byar brjod //
NK122(kho)001:178: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa yang //
NK122(kho)001:179: ye nas sangs rgyas zhes bsgrags pa //
NK122(kho)001:180: chen po lngar snang gang 'di dag /
NK122(kho)001:181: thugs rje rtag pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK122(kho)001:183: ma bcos rtog bral ye nas dag /'gro drug sems can thams cad kyis //
NK122(kho)001:184: skye dang 'tsho dang rten pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:185: rgyu dang rkyen dang gnas pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:186: mi rtog ngang gis kun 'byung bas //
NK122(kho)001:187: ngang gis rgyun gyi 'khor lor gnas //
NK122(kho)001:189: de ltar rgyud kyi theg pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:190: rang bzhin shugs kyi gdul bya ste //
NK122(kho)001:192: dam pa'i 'khor lo rab bskor nas //
NK122(kho)001:193: de nyid nyams su blang ba kun kyang mthar zag
NK122(kho)001:194: pa med pa'i dbyings 'phags pa'i lam la bkod do
NK122(kho)001:195: // dam pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis don dam nges
NK122(kho)001:196: pa'i theg pas 'dul ba'i gdul bya gtan tshigs ci'i
NK122(kho)001:199: shin tu dug gsum bdo ba yis //
NK122(kho)001:200: gdul don dam nges pa'i theg pas bar dka' ba'i sems can rnams la //
NK122(kho)001:201: bskal pa'i 'khor lo gdul bya ste //
NK122(kho)001:202: zhen dang rmongs dang 'khrugs pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:203: las ngan 'du shes ngan pa rnams //
NK122(kho)001:204: rgyun gcod bsgyur ba'i phrin las ni //
NK122(kho)001:205: dam pa'i 'khor lo bskor byas nas //
NK122(kho)001:206: 'dul bar ma gyur de dag la //
NK122(kho)001:207: bskal pa'i 'khor los las rgyun gcod //
NK122(kho)001:208: sred zhi 'tsho bral bskal pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:209: sems dang yid kyi las rgyun gcod //
NK122(kho)001:210: bzod ldan rmongs pa'i bskal pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:211: zhen pas chags pa'i las rgyun gcod //
NK122(kho)001:212: thabs 'dzin mtshon cha'i bskal pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:213: dngos pos dngos po thams cad gcod //
NK122(kho)001:214: lhag mthong me yi bskal pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:215: dngos po'i ra ba ma lus gcod //
NK122(kho)001:216: zhi gnas chu yi bskal pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:218: thogs med rlung gi bskal pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:219: shes bya thogs med kun tu bskyod //
NK122(kho)001:220: shes rab nam mkha'i bskal pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:221: mtshan ma'i rgas rgud thams cad stong //
NK122(kho)001:222: snyigs mar gyur pa'i skabs rnams su //
NK122(kho)001:223: 'dul ba rnam gnyis nub pas na //
NK122(kho)001:224: bskal sogs thugs rjes bstan pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:225: las ngan las rgyun gcod pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)001:226: sdug bsngal rnams kyi rnam par snang //
NK122(kho)001:227: 'das nas nub bo zhes pas na //
NK122(kho)001:228: ma 'das ma nub de nyid de //
NK122(kho)001:229: thugs rje'i shugs kyis 'dul ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:230: thabs dang theg pa gang dag pas //
NK122(kho)001:231: tha ma'i tha mar bshad pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:232: bar ma rgyas par bshad pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:233: srid pa'i chos rnams sdug bsngal te //
NK122(kho)001:234: thar pa 'dod pa'i skal can la //
NK122(kho)001:235: don dam nges pa'i theg pa yang //
NK122(kho)001:236: gnyen po'i thabs kyi 'dul thabs kyis //
NK122(kho)001:237: srid pa'i sdug bsngal rab bsal te //
NK122(kho)001:238: zag med dbyings la 'god pa rnams //
NK122(kho)001:239: don dam nges par brjod pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:240: de yang rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK122(kho)001:241: zhar la byung dang theg pa'o //
NK122(kho)001:242: gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud las kyang //
NK122(kho)001:243: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtog /
NK122(kho)001:244: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK122(kho)001:245: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba dang //
NK122(kho)001:246: rang bzhin gsang ba'i don rnams te //
NK122(kho)001:247: zhes gsungs phyir na bye brag tu //
NK122(kho)001:248: ma rtogs phyal ba rgyang 'phen te //
NK122(kho)001:249: log rtogs mur rtug mu stegs pa //
NK122(kho)001:251: don dam nges par mi brjod de //
NK122(kho)001:252: zhar la byung ba'i lta ba'o //
NK122(kho)001:253: ma rtogs phyal ba rgyang 'phen ni //
NK122(kho)001:254: khams gsum sems can 'di dag rnams //
NK122(kho)001:255: dge dang mi dge'i chos rnams la //
NK122(kho)001:256: 'bras bu bde dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK122(kho)001:257: yod med gang du mi rtog cing //
NK122(kho)001:258: dus kyi skye ba snga phyi dag /
NK122(kho)001:259: yod med mi rtogs tshe 'di la //
NK122(kho)001:260: skye 'tsho brten pa'i las can te //
NK122(kho)001:261: lta ba med pa'i phyal ba pa //
NK122(kho)001:262: rgyang 'phen lta ba der mtshungs la //
NK122(kho)001:263: tshe 'di'i khyad par bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)001:264: gtsang sbra la sogs spyod byed cing //
NK122(kho)001:265: 'jig rten lha yi gsang tshig brten //
NK122(kho)001:266: btsan phyug 'phen pa'i mthu stobs phyir //
NK122(kho)001:267: dmigs dang spyod pa'i khyad par can //
NK122(kho)001:268: yang dag don las gol ba dang //
NK122(kho)001:269: tshe 'di'i phan bsod bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)001:270: rgyang 'phen pa zhes grags pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:271: yang na mi shes bzhir smra ba //
NK122(kho)001:272: phyal ba dman rigs rigs ma nges //
NK122(kho)001:273: dman rigs 'jug pa'i skal med te //
NK122(kho)001:274: shes rig med par dud 'gro mtshungs //
NK122(kho)001:275: ma nges skal yod rkyen ma 'dzom //
NK122(kho)001:276: dal bcas 'byor pa med dang mtshungs //
NK122(kho)001:278: rigs chad rgyu rkyen skal med yin //
NK122(kho)001:279: 'du shes can la'ang rnam bzhi ste //
NK122(kho)001:280: ya nga rnam g.yeng zhen pa can //
NK122(kho)001:281: mos pa'i 'du shes can nyid do //
NK122(kho)001:282: ya nga rnam smin drag po yis //
NK122(kho)001:283: sdug bsngal zab par 'phen byed pas //
NK122(kho)001:284: shes ldan bltas na skyi g.ya' bas //
NK122(kho)001:285: ya nga can zhes grags pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:286: g.yeng can tshe gcig ched phyir du //
NK122(kho)001:287: khe dang grags pas blo phrogs te //
NK122(kho)001:288: g.yeng ba'i bya blag sna tshogs byed //
NK122(kho)001:289: zhen pa'i 'du shes can nyid ni //
NK122(kho)001:290: zas nor rigs rgyud ched phyir du //
NK122(kho)001:291: brtson pas 'jig rten lha la brten //
NK122(kho)001:292: mig 'phrul nor dang rdzas bsgrub cing //
NK122(kho)001:293: gzhan gyi 'du shes bsgyur bar byed //
NK122(kho)001:294: mos pa can gyi mtshan nyid ni //
NK122(kho)001:295: lta ba phyal bar gnas pa la //
NK122(kho)001:296: dkon mchog gsum la skur mi byed //
NK122(kho)001:297: sdig pa'i las la ya nga zhing //
NK122(kho)001:298: cung zad dkar po'i sa bon ldan //
NK122(kho)001:299: brgyud nas sbyong ba'i las yod pa'o //
NK122(kho)001:300: log lta can la gnyis yod de //
NK122(kho)001:301: mur rtug pa dang mu stegs so //
NK122(kho)001:302: mur rtug pa'ang rnam gnyis te //
NK122(kho)001:303: rang bzhin log dang rkyen gyis log /
NK122(kho)001:304: dang po mi dge'i rkyen med kyang //
NK122(kho)001:305: las kyis sbyangs pas log par 'dzin //
NK122(kho)001:306: dge sdig rgyu 'bras tshe snga phyi //
NK122(kho)001:307: de dag thams cad med par lta //
NK122(kho)001:308: da lta snang ba glo bur ba //
NK122(kho)001:309: rgyu rkyen med par shugs kyis snang //
NK122(kho)001:310: snod bcud kun la de ltar rtog /
NK122(kho)001:311: gnyis pa rkyen gyis log pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:312: 'od srungs rdzogs byed la sogs pas //
NK122(kho)001:313: lta ba yongs su 'dzin pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:314: dkar nag rnam smin med smra zhing //
NK122(kho)001:315: skye ba snga phyi med par smra //
NK122(kho)001:316: de nyid rang gi grub mthar 'dod //
NK122(kho)001:317: phyi ma med phyir mur rtug ste //
NK122(kho)001:319: mu stegs pa yi lta ba ni //
NK122(kho)001:320: bye brag bzhi ru shes bya ste //
NK122(kho)001:321: phra men spyod dang rten log 'chal //
NK122(kho)001:322: rtags tsam 'dzin dang lung phyogs brten //
NK122(kho)001:323: bye brag bzhi po 'di dag gis //
NK122(kho)001:325: ngan song gsum gyi 'jigs pa las //
NK122(kho)001:327: lta log lta spyod ya char 'gyur //
NK122(kho)001:329: kun tu tshol ba'i lam du zhugs //
NK122(kho)001:330: phra men spyod pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK122(kho)001:331: thar pa 'dod cing bdag tu lta //
NK122(kho)001:332: mtho ris bzheng phyir mi dge bsgrub //
NK122(kho)001:333: phyin ci log pa bzhi la gnas //
NK122(kho)001:334: 'di dag kun la dngos por smra //
NK122(kho)001:335: 'dod dang lta spyod mi mtshungs pas //
NK122(kho)001:336: phra men spyad ces de la bya //
NK122(kho)001:337: rten log 'chal ba'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK122(kho)001:338: tshangs pa la sogs lha chen dag /
NK122(kho)001:339: bsod nams sbyangs pa'i stobs las byung //
NK122(kho)001:340: sbyangs stobs che bas mnga' dbang brnyes //
NK122(kho)001:341: byang chub sems dpa' mthu chen de //
NK122(kho)001:343: log lta can gyis ma shes te //
NK122(kho)001:344: phya dang dbang phyug ming btags nas //
NK122(kho)001:345: de dag rang rgyud ye grub smra //
NK122(kho)001:347: me lnga bsten dang dbyug gu dang //
NK122(kho)001:348: khyi yi dka' thub la sogs kyis //
NK122(kho)001:349: log pa'i brtul zhugs sna tshogs byed //
NK122(kho)001:350: dug gsum rdul dang mun pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:351: snying stobs dag gi bye brag las //
NK122(kho)001:352: cha mnyam mi mnyam khyad par gyis //
NK122(kho)001:353: rgyu dang 'bras bu yin par smra //
NK122(kho)001:354: rin chen gsum la rten log nas //
NK122(kho)001:356: 'chal ba'i spyod pa sna tshogs byed //
NK122(kho)001:357: thob bya'i 'bras bu mi thob ste //
NK122(kho)001:358: sdug bsngal can du phal cher gzhol //
NK122(kho)001:359: rten log 'chal ba'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK122(kho)001:360: rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK122(kho)001:361: sprul pa snga ma 'das pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:362: bstan pa'i snyigs mar gyur pa'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:363: bstan pa de yi gzugs brnyan la //
NK122(kho)001:365: shes rab gsum la ma sbyangs pas //
NK122(kho)001:366: bstan pa'i don la rtog dpyod byas //
NK122(kho)001:367: bden gnyis brjod bya'i don ma phig /
NK122(kho)001:368: zab mo'i don la zhen phyogs drangs //
NK122(kho)001:369: de gang yin zhe na rig byed kyi bu lhag
NK122(kho)001:370: spyod la sogs dang sgyu rtsal shes kyi bu ring
NK122(kho)001:372: log par smra ba mang du byung //
NK122(kho)001:373: mu stegs kyi ston pa drug gsum bco brgyad ces bya ba lta ba dang grub mtha'/
NK122(kho)001:374: la ci 'dra byung na la rgyu las 'bras tshe snga phyi thams cad med nas 'gog pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:375: nyi tshe ba'i stong pa chad lta kho nar bltas so //
NK122(kho)001:376: la las yod par rnam par brtags pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:377: 'bras bu rtag par rtog pa'i dngos po rang brgyud de rtag par lta'o mtshan mar smras //
NK122(kho)001:378: de dag gis bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan rin po che ci'i phyir mi rtogs zhe na pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:379: zab cing gsung rab 'di rgya mtsho ltar rgya che
NK122(kho)001:380: dgongs pa sna tshogs bstan pa gang zag gis mi
NK122(kho)001:382: yin snyam rang gis dpyod gyi pas bka' zab mo'i don ma phig ste //
NK122(kho)001:383: log pa'i lta ba rtag chad sna tshogs 'dzin //
NK122(kho)001:384: rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i mu stegs pa des sems ni
NK122(kho)001:385: log pa'i lam du zhugs te rtag chad kyi don
NK122(kho)001:386: la gnas shing nyon mongs pa rang gar spyod pa'i
NK122(kho)001:387: // lus kyi sangs rgyas rtags chos gos rnam gsum la sogs pa 'dzin pas //
NK122(kho)001:388: rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i mu stegs pa ces de la bya'o //
NK122(kho)001:389: sprul sku sh+aakya seng ge'i bstan pa rgas te 'jigs la nye bas //
NK122(kho)001:390: snyigs ma'i lnga dus la deng sang bab ste gong gi //
NK122(kho)001:392: deng sang nang pa'i sangs rgyas pa nang na shin tu mang bar gsungs so //
NK122(kho)001:393: lung gi rgyud sde bzhi dang sde snod gsum gyi
NK122(kho)001:394: phyogs tsam 'dzin par byed cing lta ba rtag chad
NK122(kho)001:396: rgyal ba'i bka' yi zhar byung gi theg pa yin bas //
NK122(kho)001:397: phyogs ni mthun pa tsam gyi sgra rjes su 'brel
NK122(kho)001:398: bas mu stegs de dag gi mtshan nyid rgyas par
NK122(kho)001:399: bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa ni lta ba log
NK122(kho)001:400: pa ste // grangs mthun pa las don nor pa song nas //
NK122(kho)001:401: zhen rang gis 'dod pa'i phyogs kyis 'khrul pa'i lam du zhugs nas //
NK122(kho)001:402: de'i nga rgyal gyis snyems pas de las bzlog par dka' ba'o //
NK122(kho)001:403: lung gi phyogs tsam 'dzin pa'i mu stegs pa de yang bye brag rnam bzhi ste //
NK122(kho)001:404: phyi rol pa dang yang dag pa //
NK122(kho)001:405: gsang sngags pa dang gsang chen te //
NK122(kho)001:406: phyi rol pa yang rnam pa gsum //
NK122(kho)001:407: bye brag pa dang tha snyad pa //
NK122(kho)001:408: rang snang phyogs gcig zhes bya ste //
NK122(kho)001:409: nyan thos bye brag mdo sde pa //
NK122(kho)001:410: rang sangs rgyas kyi lta ba las //
NK122(kho)001:411: cha mthun zhen pa log par song //
NK122(kho)001:412: yang dag pa yang rnam gsum ste //
NK122(kho)001:413: phra ba zab pa rgya che yangs //
NK122(kho)001:414: 'di dag sems tsam rnam bden rdzun //
NK122(kho)001:415: dbu ma chen po'i lta ba las //
NK122(kho)001:416: cha mthun tsam gyis log par song //
NK122(kho)001:417: spyod pa phyogs mthun tsam du zhugs //
NK122(kho)001:418: ci tsam zab mo'i tshig brjod kyang //
NK122(kho)001:419: bdag 'dzin gnyis po ma spangs pas //
NK122(kho)001:420: bsam gtan nor ba'i lam du zhugs //
NK122(kho)001:421: rtsa ba 'di las gyes pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:422: log pa'i lta ba du ma byung //
NK122(kho)001:423: gsang sngags pa la'ang rnam gsum ste //
NK122(kho)001:424: rig byed rig spyod rig sbyor ba //
NK122(kho)001:425: bya ba spyod pa rnal 'byor las //
NK122(kho)001:426: lta ba spyod pa bsam gtan dag /
NK122(kho)001:427: cha mthun tsam ste don las log /'dzin pa zhen 'khrul mtha' la zhen //
NK122(kho)001:428: bder gshegs sprul sku'i snang ba las //
NK122(kho)001:429: phya dang dbang phyug dag tu 'khrul //
NK122(kho)001:430: rig byed smrang 'don la sogs pas //
NK122(kho)001:431: dka' thub dka' spyad ci bsgrub kyang //
NK122(kho)001:432: zhen pa'i mun pa ma dwangs pas //
NK122(kho)001:433: 'khor ba nyid du skye mang brgyud //
NK122(kho)001:434: lta ba 'di las gyes pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:435: log pa'i lta ba du ma byung //
NK122(kho)001:436: gsang chen pa yang rnam gsum ste //
NK122(kho)001:437: brtul zhugs cher spyod pa dang ni //
NK122(kho)001:438: rgyal dpog pa dang rgyal thabs pa //
NK122(kho)001:439: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs chen las //
NK122(kho)001:440: lta ba spyod pa ting 'dzin dag /'dra mthun tsam gyi ltos 'khrul te //
NK122(kho)001:441: bde gshegs longs sku'i gzugs brnyan las //
NK122(kho)001:442: seng ge dang ni 'phrog byed dang //
NK122(kho)001:443: dbyig gi snying po dag tu 'khrul //
NK122(kho)001:444: 'dra mthun spyod pa ci spyad kyang //
NK122(kho)001:445: sgro 'dogs zhen pa ma spangs pas //
NK122(kho)001:446: thar pa'i 'bras bu mi myong ste //
NK122(kho)001:447: lta spyod log pa'i dka' thub can //
NK122(kho)001:448: bsam pas 'bras bu dag par bzhed //
NK122(kho)001:449: rang rgyud spyod pa sna tshogs spyod //
NK122(kho)001:450: 'di dag ya mtshan can zhes grags //
NK122(kho)001:451: de dag so so'i dbye ba yang //
NK122(kho)001:452: mdo tsam rab tu brjod bya ste //
NK122(kho)001:453: brtul zhugs pa ni gsang sngags kyi //
NK122(kho)001:454: thabs kyis zin pa'i spyod pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:455: bdag gzhan gnyis kyi don bsgrub pa //
NK122(kho)001:456: de yang cha mthun tsam las 'khrul //
NK122(kho)001:457: mnyam pa'i lta ba ma rtogs shing //
NK122(kho)001:458: brtul zhugs spyod pa cha mthun spyod //
NK122(kho)001:459: bdag gzhan gnyis ka chud gzan te //
NK122(kho)001:460: phal cher mtho ris mi myong na //
NK122(kho)001:461: thar pa'i 'bras bu ga la srid //
NK122(kho)001:462: log brtags zhen pa'i mthu brtas pas //
NK122(kho)001:463: 'jig rten dngos grub phra mo dag /'byung bar 'gyur zhing ya mtshan skye //
NK122(kho)001:464: rgyal dpog rjes su rnal 'byor las //
NK122(kho)001:465: cha mthun tsam gyis 'khrul pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:466: chos dbyings nam mkha' mu med las //
NK122(kho)001:467: gtso bo bem po nyid du 'khrul //
NK122(kho)001:468: med las mi zad ye shes las //
NK122(kho)001:469: nang gi skyes bu byed par 'khrul //
NK122(kho)001:470: zab pa'i tshul du smra byas kyang //
NK122(kho)001:471: yang dag don chen ma rtogs pas //
NK122(kho)001:473: lta ba 'di yi bye brag las //
NK122(kho)001:474: zab bcos lta ba grangs mang byung //
NK122(kho)001:475: phal cher da lta'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK122(kho)001:476: sgom chen rnams kyi nang na mang //
NK122(kho)001:477: rgyal thabs shin tu rnal 'byor las //
NK122(kho)001:478: cha mthun tsam gyis 'khrul pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:479: de dag kun gyi lta ba ni //
NK122(kho)001:480: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i rten 'brel dang //
NK122(kho)001:481: don dam rten med brten pa med //
NK122(kho)001:482: gang zag sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK122(kho)001:483: bdag gcig yod de mngon ma gyur //
NK122(kho)001:484: 'di zhes bya ba'i khas len med //
NK122(kho)001:485: khams gsum sems can 'di dag rnams //
NK122(kho)001:486: kun rdzob don dam gong ma bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:487: kun gyi sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK122(kho)001:488: bdag re yod de mngon ma gyur //
NK122(kho)001:489: dkar nag las kyi rnam smin dag /'dod na yod de mi 'dod med //
NK122(kho)001:490: 'bras bu mngon du thob pa'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:491: rig pa med pas ye shes med //
NK122(kho)001:492: dngos po med pas dwangs pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:493: bcud med nam mkha' dwangs pa ltar //
NK122(kho)001:494: gyur na chos sku yin zhes smra //
NK122(kho)001:495: bder gshegs thugs rje'i mdzad pa rnams //
NK122(kho)001:496: rig pa med pas thugs rje med //
NK122(kho)001:497: snang nyid sgyu ma'i skyes bu mtshungs //
NK122(kho)001:498: phal cher rang gis brtags par snang //
NK122(kho)001:499: de 'dra lta ba'i bye brag rnams //
NK122(kho)001:500: cha mthun log pa mang po byung //
NK122(kho)001:501: rgyu nyid chad par rtog pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:502: rgyu yi phyogs gcig chad par rtog /'bras bu chad par rtog pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:503: 'bras bu phyogs gcig chad par rtog /
NK122(kho)001:504: rgyu 'bras kun tu chad par rtog /
NK122(kho)001:505: chad par lta ba'i rnam grangs yin //
NK122(kho)001:506: rgyu nyid rtag par rtog pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:507: rgyu yi phyogs gcig rtag par rtog /'bras bu rtag par rtog pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:508: 'bras bu'i phyogs gcig rtag par rtog /
NK122(kho)001:509: rgyu 'bras kun tu rtag par rtog /
NK122(kho)001:510: rtag par lta ba'i rnam grangs yin //
NK122(kho)001:511: rtag dang chad pa'i bye brag rnams //
NK122(kho)001:512: log lta can gyi rnam grangs te //
NK122(kho)001:513: bla med theg pa las log yin //
NK122(kho)001:514: lta ba'i bye brag gong ma 'di //
NK122(kho)001:515: da dus snyigs ma'i deng sang la //
NK122(kho)001:516: gsang sngags theg par khas 'ches pa'i //
NK122(kho)001:517: shes rab gnyis la ma sbyangs pa //
NK122(kho)001:518: de dag kun gyi nang na'ang mang //
NK122(kho)001:519: log pa'i lta ba zab mo dag /
NK122(kho)001:520: shin tu zab pa'i tshul smras kyang //
NK122(kho)001:521: zhen pa'i mtha' gnyis ma spangs pas //
NK122(kho)001:522: srid pa'i gnas su yang yang 'khor //
NK122(kho)001:523: bsam gtan bye brag kha cig gis //
NK122(kho)001:525: skye mched bzhi sogs skyes nas ni //
NK122(kho)001:526: sngon du mkhas la ma brten pas //
NK122(kho)001:527: 'bras bu nyid du yang dag blang //
NK122(kho)001:528: las kyi bag chags ma zad pas //
NK122(kho)001:530: dkon mchog gsum la skur pa btab //
NK122(kho)001:531: mnar med gnas su ltung ba'ang mang //
NK122(kho)001:532: 'di dag kun gyi bye brag ni //
NK122(kho)001:533: mdo rgyud kun la rgya cher yang //
NK122(kho)001:534: tshig tshogs mang pos 'jigs pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)001:535: mdor bstan tsam las ma brjod do //
NK122(kho)001:536: phyi rol lta ba 'di dag rnams //
NK122(kho)001:537: 'khor lo rgyun gyi gdul bya ste //
NK122(kho)001:538: sems la rtog pa thob pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:539: 'bras bu tshol ba'i zhen phyogs can //
NK122(kho)001:540: kha cig sangs rgyas snga ma yi //
NK122(kho)001:541: bstan pa rgas par gyur pa'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:542: rtog dpyod log par 'khrul pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:543: log par gyur pa 'ga' zhig ni //
NK122(kho)001:544: sangs rgyas slob ma thabs mkhas pas //
NK122(kho)001:545: skal dman thabs kyis gzhug pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)001:546: lam tshol pa yi thabs su bstan //
NK122(kho)001:547: zhar las byung ba zhes kyang bya //
NK122(kho)001:548: sangs rgyas nye gnas zhes kyang bya //
NK122(kho)001:549: lung las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK122(kho)001:550: mu stegs can la smad ci bya //
NK122(kho)001:551: rnam par snang mdzad ring ba'i rgyu //
NK122(kho)001:552: zhes gsungs phyir na zhar byung ngo //
NK122(kho)001:553: theg gsum dam pa'i dam pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:554: don dam nges pa'i theg pa yang //
NK122(kho)001:555: bye brag rnam pa gsum nyid de //
NK122(kho)001:557: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:558: gdul bya'i phyogs kyang gsum nyid de //
NK122(kho)001:559: blo yi skal pa che chung las //
NK122(kho)001:560: dman dang 'bring dang chen po yin //
NK122(kho)001:561: de yi 'dul thabs de bzhin te //
NK122(kho)001:562: gnyen pos spangs dang thabs kyis bsgyur //
NK122(kho)001:563: ye shes chen po'i gnas su dag /
NK122(kho)001:564: gdul bya 'dul thabs theg pa gsum //
NK122(kho)001:565: so sor sprad de sdeb par bya //
NK122(kho)001:566: bye brag rgyas par bshad pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:567: theg gsum re re'ang gsum gsum ste //
NK122(kho)001:568: tha ma 'bring dang mchog gi tshul //
NK122(kho)001:569: des na theg pa dgu zhes grags //
NK122(kho)001:570: rig pa mchog 'bring tha ma'i phyir //
NK122(kho)001:571: gdul bya gsum la'ang gsum gsum ste //
NK122(kho)001:572: snod kyi bye brag rnam pa dgu //
NK122(kho)001:573: gdul bya dgu zhes rab tu grags //
NK122(kho)001:574: thabs kyang de bzhin bye brag dgu //
NK122(kho)001:575: dgu gsum nyi shu bdun du sdeb //
NK122(kho)001:576: dang po gsum yang 'di lta ste //
NK122(kho)001:577: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems //
NK122(kho)001:578: gdul bya dman dang 'bring po dang //
NK122(kho)001:579: de bzhin mchog gi bye brag gis //
NK122(kho)001:580: nyon mongs spangs dang 'geg dang sbyong //
NK122(kho)001:581: 'dul thabs gsum du rnam par bshad //
NK122(kho)001:582: tha ma'i tha ma'ang 'di lta ste //
NK122(kho)001:584: spyod dang tshul khrims lam gyi yun //
NK122(kho)001:585: 'bras bu dag dang bdun du shes //
NK122(kho)001:586: mi rta ga sdug bsngal stong bdag med //
NK122(kho)001:587: bdag gtsang skyid rtag las bzlog pa //
NK122(kho)001:588: sangs rgyas theg pa spyi yi sgo //
NK122(kho)001:590: nyan thos theg pa'i 'jug sgo yin //
NK122(kho)001:591: snod bcud rdul phran sil bu dang //
NK122(kho)001:592: skad cig cha med nang gi sems //
NK122(kho)001:593: de la sogs pa'i bye brag ni //
NK122(kho)001:594: nyan thos theg pa'i lta ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:595: bden pa bzhi dang dbugs bgrangs 1ngang //
NK122(kho)001:596: zad par brgyad dang keng rus sogs //
NK122(kho)001:597: de dag bsam gtan bye brag yin //
NK122(kho)001:598: shin tu ya nga'i las spangs te //
NK122(kho)001:599: zhen pa'i dge ba phun sum tshogs //
NK122(kho)001:600: khrus dang gtsang sbra la sogs pas //
NK122(kho)001:601: gang yang kun rdzob mtshan ma'i tshul //
NK122(kho)001:602: thams cad spang blang dgag sgrub pa //
NK122(kho)001:603: nyan thos theg pa'i spyod pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:604: so sor thar pa'i rigs bdun te //
NK122(kho)001:605: sdom pa'i rtsa ba bcu gsum dang //
NK122(kho)001:606: nyis brgya lnga bcu lnga brgya dang //
NK122(kho)001:607: bslab pa'i gzhi lnga rdzogs pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:608: nyan thos bsrung ba'i tshul khrims yin //
NK122(kho)001:609: 'jug nas sred pa zad kyi bar //
NK122(kho)001:610: bskal pa chen po brgya sogs yin //
NK122(kho)001:611: 'bras bu srid pa'i sdug bsngal zad //
NK122(kho)001:612: dgra bcom skyes bu zung bzhi yin //
NK122(kho)001:613: lung las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK122(kho)001:614: shin tu ya nga'i las spangs te //
NK122(kho)001:616: rang gi bsam pa de bsgrub pas //
NK122(kho)001:617: so sor thar pa'i lam du snang //
NK122(kho)001:618: zhes gsungs lung gis bgrod dang gsal //
NK122(kho)001:619: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:621: lta ba phyi rol rdul phran la //
NK122(kho)001:622: gzugs kyi phung po bdag med pa'o //
NK122(kho)001:623: mar me rgyun zad lta bu ni //
NK122(kho)001:624: ma rig zad nas 'du byed zad //
NK122(kho)001:625: de nas rga shi'i bar du ste //
NK122(kho)001:626: de ltar zhen pa gnyis dgag pa //
NK122(kho)001:627: bsam gtan yin pa rgyal bas gsungs //
NK122(kho)001:628: spyod pa tshul khrims nyan thos dang //
NK122(kho)001:629: mthun par 'jug la khyad par du //
NK122(kho)001:630: gcig pur gnas pa sgrub pa'o //
NK122(kho)001:631: bskal pa chen po brgya yi bar //
NK122(kho)001:632: rgyal ba'i bka' la rab sbyangs pas //
NK122(kho)001:633: chos nyid rim gyis rtogs gyur kyang //
NK122(kho)001:634: smon lam rgya chen ma btab pas //
NK122(kho)001:635: 'bras bu thob daka'i skye ba la //
NK122(kho)001:636: dge ba'i bshes gnyen ma bsten par //
NK122(kho)001:637: chu zla la sogs rkyen rnams kyis //
NK122(kho)001:638: rtog tshig nyams su blang ba'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:639: bden pa mthong zhing srid pa zad //
NK122(kho)001:640: yid bzhin bde mchog sa la gnas //
NK122(kho)001:641: slad kyi 'gro don mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:642: lus kyi sprul pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK122(kho)001:643: sangs rgyas byang chub mi bzhugs pa'i //
NK122(kho)001:644: bar skabs dag tu don mdzad pa'ang //
NK122(kho)001:645: gsung gi chos 'chad mi mkhyen par //
NK122(kho)001:646: sprul pa'i thabs kyi don mdzad pa'o //
NK122(kho)001:647: rang sangs rgyas su rnam par grags //
NK122(kho)001:648: lung las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK122(kho)001:650: bdag med chos gcig med mthong bas //
NK122(kho)001:651: brjod med sprul pas chos rnams ston //
NK122(kho)001:652: zhes gsungs phyir na lung gis gsal //
NK122(kho)001:653: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:654: dbang po tha ma'i mchog gyur rnams //
NK122(kho)001:655: bden pa gnyis po 'jug pa'i sgo //
NK122(kho)001:656: 'di dag rtogs pa'i lta ba ni //
NK122(kho)001:657: lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo las kyang //
NK122(kho)001:658: don rab 'byed pa'i bsam gtan dang //
NK122(kho)001:659: de bzhin nyid dmigs bsam gtan dang //
NK122(kho)001:660: de ltar lung gi gtan tshig gis //
NK122(kho)001:661: kun rdzob tsam du 'jig rten yod //
NK122(kho)001:662: don dam du ni rang bzhin med //
NK122(kho)001:663: phyi rol gnas dang nang 'di kun //
NK122(kho)001:664: yul rnams sems kyi 'khrul smra zhing //
NK122(kho)001:665: sems nyid dus matha'i skad cig ma //
NK122(kho)001:666: skad cig mi rtag rgyun gyi gnas //
NK122(kho)001:667: gang yang bden pa gnyis smra ba //
NK122(kho)001:668: rnam rig gnyis kyi lta ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:669: yul sems so sor rkyen gyis snang //
NK122(kho)001:670: yul rnams phra rags rdul cha ste //
NK122(kho)001:671: phyogs char gzhig na dngos po med //
NK122(kho)001:672: sems nyid thog matha'i skad cig ma //
NK122(kho)001:673: dus gsum gzhig na rang bzhin med //
NK122(kho)001:674: rkyen ni gnyis dang bzhi dag gis //
NK122(kho)001:675: snod bcud gnyis su snang ba'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:676: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam //
NK122(kho)001:677: bden pa gnyis su phye ba yang //
NK122(kho)001:678: de nyid gzhan du brjod med tshul //
NK122(kho)001:679: de 'dra lta ba'i bye brag rnams //
NK122(kho)001:680: mdo sde spyod pa'i lta ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:681: ma rig 'khrul pa'i bag chags kyis //
NK122(kho)001:682: mig gi rab rib snang ba bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:683: phyi rol gnas dang nang 'di kun //
NK122(kho)001:684: mi bden bden ltar kun la snang //
NK122(kho)001:685: 'khrul pa'i bag chags ma zad tshe //
NK122(kho)001:686: nam yang khegs par 'gyur ba min //
NK122(kho)001:687: nad zad rab rib dwangs pa bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:688: 'khrul pa'i bag chags thams cad zad //
NK122(kho)001:689: thim pa med pa yul dang bral //
NK122(kho)001:690: gzhan song med par mngon 'khrul dwangs //
NK122(kho)001:691: 'khrul rig mnyam du zad smra ba //
NK122(kho)001:692: dbu ma'i lta ba kha gcig bzhed //
NK122(kho)001:693: kha cig phyi nang snod bcud dag /
NK122(kho)001:694: bden pa gnyis su gnas pa las //
NK122(kho)001:695: snod ni sems kyi 'khrul pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:696: sems ni skad cig dus gsum bral //
NK122(kho)001:697: de nyid don dam bden pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:698: kun rdzob sgyu mar mi 'gags te //
NK122(kho)001:700: sems nyid dus gsum skad cig ma //
NK122(kho)001:701: 'gag pa med pa kun rdzob yin //
NK122(kho)001:702: bden pa gnyis kyi bye brag kyang //
NK122(kho)001:703: ldog phyogs tsam gyis tha dad pa //
NK122(kho)001:704: dbu ma'i lta ba kha cig bzhed //
NK122(kho)001:705: de dag tsam min rim pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:706: don rab 'byed pa'i bsam gtan no //
NK122(kho)001:707: don min cig char 'jug pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:708: phyi dang nang 'di thams cad kun //
NK122(kho)001:709: kun rdzob tsam du 'jig rten yod //
NK122(kho)001:710: sgyu ma'i 'khrul pa ji bzhin te //
NK122(kho)001:711: don dam 'gag pa med pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)001:712: 'gro drug sems can thams cad kun //
NK122(kho)001:713: bag chags mthun pa'i snang ba ni //
NK122(kho)001:714: rang rang bsags pa ltar snang ngo //
NK122(kho)001:715: don dam gang la'ang dngos gzhi med //
NK122(kho)001:716: smra bsam las 'das ye shes yul //
NK122(kho)001:717: mtshan nyid gsum ldan don dam pa //
NK122(kho)001:718: bsgrub tshe mnyam par bzhag pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:719: rjes la sgyu ma lta bu yis //
NK122(kho)001:720: zhen chags bral ba'i spyod pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:721: kun rdzob snying rjes gnas pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:722: sems bskyed nas bzung mthar thug bar //
NK122(kho)001:723: gzhal dang sgom pas nyams su len //
NK122(kho)001:724: tshe gcig don dam bden pa gzigs //
NK122(kho)001:725: dbu ma'i lta ba kha cig bzhed //
NK122(kho)001:726: de dag la sogs bden pa gnyis //
NK122(kho)001:727: ris su dbye bar byed pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:728: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam //
NK122(kho)001:729: sbyin sogs pha rol phyin pa la //
NK122(kho)001:730: spyod pa byang chub lta ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:731: bsam gtan mnyam par bzhag pa'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:732: nam mkha' lta bur spros dang bral //
NK122(kho)001:733: rjes la sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam //
NK122(kho)001:734: zhen med tshul gyis gsal bar smra //
NK122(kho)001:735: byams dang snying rje rnam sbyong ba //
NK122(kho)001:736: byang chub sems dpa'i bsam gtan yin //
NK122(kho)001:737: sbyin sogs rnam par dkar ba'i las //
NK122(kho)001:738: zhen med tshul gyis spyod pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:739: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:740: rtsa ba bzhi dang nyi shu dang //
NK122(kho)001:741: sdom pa'i bye brag mtha' yas pa //
NK122(kho)001:742: bsrung ba tshul khrims yin par bstan //
NK122(kho)001:743: byang chub sems dpa' rang gi'o //
NK122(kho)001:744: so sor thar pa'i sdom pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:745: bye brag rnam pa mtha' yas kyang //
NK122(kho)001:746: rten nam snod kyi tshul gyi phyir //
NK122(kho)001:747: byang sems yan lag sdom pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:748: grangs med bskal pa gsum dag gis //
NK122(kho)001:749: sems bskyed nas bzung sangs rgyas par //
NK122(kho)001:750: sgrib sbyong ye shes rdzogs tshul gyis //
NK122(kho)001:751: rim gyis 'jug pa yun gyi tshad //
NK122(kho)001:752: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa //
NK122(kho)001:753: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:754: mthar phyin pa yi 'bras bur bzhed //
NK122(kho)001:755: lung las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK122(kho)001:756: yul med ma skyes phyogs dang bral //
NK122(kho)001:757: bdag med byams snyoms rtog las 'das //
NK122(kho)001:758: sa dang rnam thar bde bskrun pas //
NK122(kho)001:759: dngos med ngo bo nyid sku thob //
NK122(kho)001:760: ces gsungs lung gi bgrod dang gsal //
NK122(kho)001:761: dka' thub rig byed theg pa yang //
NK122(kho)001:762: yul gyi rnam pa gsum nyid de //
NK122(kho)001:763: bya ba spyod pa rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK122(kho)001:764: gdul bya'i blo shed bye brag gis //
NK122(kho)001:765: 'bring po nyid la rnam gsum ste //
NK122(kho)001:766: tha ma 'bring dang mchog tu snang //
NK122(kho)001:767: 'dul thabs de bzhin bye brag gsum //
NK122(kho)001:768: bya ba rgyud kyi theg pa yang //
NK122(kho)001:770: spyod dang dam tshig lam gyi yun //
NK122(kho)001:771: 'bras bu dag dang bdun du bzhed //
NK122(kho)001:772: gsang sngags spyi yi 'jug sgo ni //
NK122(kho)001:773: bden gnyis dbyer med sgo nas 'jug /
NK122(kho)001:774: khyad par bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni //
NK122(kho)001:775: lus ngag yid gsum rnam dag pa //
NK122(kho)001:776: sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin 'jug /
NK122(kho)001:777: lta ba snod bcud chos 'di rnams //
NK122(kho)001:778: don dam spros mtha' bral ba las //
NK122(kho)001:779: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid 'di //
NK122(kho)001:780: 'khrul pa'i ngo la cir snang yang //
NK122(kho)001:781: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK122(kho)001:782: 'bras bu'i ngo bo ye nas gnas //
NK122(kho)001:783: chu dang gsher ba ji bzhin no //
NK122(kho)001:784: bden gnyis ye nas dbyer med pa //
NK122(kho)001:785: gsang sngags spyi yi lta ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:786: bya ba'i rnal 'byor bsam gtan ni //
NK122(kho)001:787: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs //
NK122(kho)001:788: drug gis 'jug pa'i tshul nyid kyis //
NK122(kho)001:789: lha yi dkyil 'khor gsal ba las //
NK122(kho)001:790: ye shes sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK122(kho)001:791: bkur 'os rje bo'i tshul nyid du //
NK122(kho)001:792: mdun gyi mkha' la spyan drangs te //
NK122(kho)001:793: phyag 'tshal la sogs yan lag bdun //
NK122(kho)001:794: bsod nams tshul gyi yongs bsags shing //
NK122(kho)001:795: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa rgyun mi bcad //
NK122(kho)001:796: dngos grub blangs te gtang rag gsol //
NK122(kho)001:797: bya ba'i ting 'dzin rim pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:798: bya ba'i rgyud kyi spyod pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:799: dag pa gsum gyi mtha' bzung nas //
NK122(kho)001:800: khrus dang gtsang sbra bder spyod nas //
NK122(kho)001:801: zhag grangs dus tshig gza' rgyu skar //
NK122(kho)001:802: gtsang ma'i yo byad la sogs pa //
NK122(kho)001:804: bya bas bsrung ba'i tshul khrims ni //
NK122(kho)001:805: so sor thar dang byang chub sems //
NK122(kho)001:806: spyi yi sdom brtson mi bshig cing //
NK122(kho)001:807: lus ngag yid gsum dam tshig dag /'da' bar mi byed yan lag bcas //
NK122(kho)001:808: bye brag tshul gyis gnas pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:810: ring mthar mi tshe bcu drug gis //
NK122(kho)001:811: rgyal rigs bram ze gtsang ma dang //
NK122(kho)001:812: 'dod pa'i lha dang gzugs kyi khams //
NK122(kho)001:813: gtsang ma'i lus 'dzin gsang sngags kyi //
NK122(kho)001:814: theg pa chen po bsgrub par 'gyur //
NK122(kho)001:815: bcu drug mtha' la zag bral nas //
NK122(kho)001:816: rang gi lha yi sku nyid kyi //
NK122(kho)001:818: rnam dag zhing du rab snang ste //
NK122(kho)001:819: brgya phrag bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK122(kho)001:820: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa non te //
NK122(kho)001:822: lung las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK122(kho)001:823: lus ngag yid gsum rnam dag pas //
NK122(kho)001:824: khrus dang gtsang sbra bder spyod te //
NK122(kho)001:827: zhes gsungs lung gis bgrod dang sla //
NK122(kho)001:828: spyod pa'i rnal 'byor bye brag bdun //
NK122(kho)001:830: 'jug sgo spyod dang dam tshig gsum //
NK122(kho)001:831: bya ba'i rnal 'byor dag dang mtshungs //
NK122(kho)001:833: bsam gtan rnam snang ting 'dzin las //
NK122(kho)001:834: de nyid bzhi yi tshul dag gis //
NK122(kho)001:835: bsnyen sgrub yan lag rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK122(kho)001:836: zag bcas sa la mi tshe bdun //
NK122(kho)001:837: skye ba gong dang 'dra ba las //
NK122(kho)001:838: de mthar zag gsum zad gyur nas //
NK122(kho)001:840: bsam gtan lam la rnam gnas te //
NK122(kho)001:841: brgya phrag bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK122(kho)001:842: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gi sa //
NK122(kho)001:843: 'bras bu thob pa gdon mi za //
NK122(kho)001:844: 'di skad lung las gsungs pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:845: bya ba dag gi las spyod de //
NK122(kho)001:847: mi g.yo sems dpa' mngon sum du //
NK122(kho)001:849: zhes gsungs lung gis bgrod dang gsal //
NK122(kho)001:850: rnal 'byor theg pa rnam pa bdun //
NK122(kho)001:852: phyi rol nang dang gnas 'di kun //
NK122(kho)001:853: yul dngos ma skyes chos kyi dbyings //
NK122(kho)001:854: 'dzin pa bdag med ye shes ngang //
NK122(kho)001:855: de nyid ye nas dbyer med pa //
NK122(kho)001:856: rnal 'byor zhes bya'i lta ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:857: bye brag rgya chen gzhan du btsal //
NK122(kho)001:858: mngon par byang chub rnam lnga yis //
NK122(kho)001:859: rang gi lha yi sku bskyed de //
NK122(kho)001:860: cho 'phrul bzhi yis rgyud sbyangs nas //
NK122(kho)001:861: ye shes dam tshig dbyer med pa //
NK122(kho)001:863: rnal 'byor theg pa'i spyod pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:864: sems kyi spyod pa'i cho 'phrul te //
NK122(kho)001:865: ngag gi spyod pa sngags dang dbyangs //
NK122(kho)001:866: lus kyi spyod pa gar phyag rgya //
NK122(kho)001:867: de dag 'dzoms pas sgrub pa la //
NK122(kho)001:868: rdzas dang yo byad gtsor ma gsungs //
NK122(kho)001:869: 'byor pa'i tshogs ni mchog tu bshad //
NK122(kho)001:870: bsrung ba'i tshul khrims bye brag ni //
NK122(kho)001:871: 'og ma rnams dang ldan bzhin du //
NK122(kho)001:872: rigs lnga'i dam tshig mchog tu bshad //
NK122(kho)001:873: sdom gsum mi spangs bde gshegs rigs //
NK122(kho)001:874: bla ma rdo rje dril bu ldan //
NK122(kho)001:875: rtag tu bkur 'chang rdo rje'i rigs //
NK122(kho)001:876: chos dang zang zing mi 'jigs byams //
NK122(kho)001:877: sbyin gsum ldan pa rin chen rigs //
NK122(kho)001:878: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:879: mnyam bsam pad+mo rigs kyi dam //
NK122(kho)001:880: 'phags tshogs rtag tu mchod pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:881: las kyi rigs kyi dam tshig go //
NK122(kho)001:882: de dag bsrung bya'i dam tshig yin //
NK122(kho)001:883: mi tshe gsum gyi nang rol tu //
NK122(kho)001:885: las dang nyon mongs kun byang nas //
NK122(kho)001:886: khams gsum 'jigs sogs zag pa bral //
NK122(kho)001:887: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad du //
NK122(kho)001:888: phra rags shes bya'i sgrib byang nas //
NK122(kho)001:889: stug po bkod pa'i sa non te //
NK122(kho)001:890: rdzogs sangs rgyas su nges par 'gyur //
NK122(kho)001:891: lung las kyang ni 'di skad gsungs //
NK122(kho)001:892: sems nyid yul las rtsal rdzogs te //
NK122(kho)001:893: yul nyid rigs pas mngon mthong nas //
NK122(kho)001:894: de nyid der ni mngon byas nas //
NK122(kho)001:895: rnal 'byor stug po bkod pa'i sa //
NK122(kho)001:896: zhes gsungs lung gis bgrod dang gsal //
NK122(kho)001:897: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa yang //
NK122(kho)001:898: gdul bya'i blo sher khyad par gyis //
NK122(kho)001:899: rnam pa gsum du snang ba ste //
NK122(kho)001:900: bskyed dang rdzogs dang shin tu rdzogs //
NK122(kho)001:901: tha ma bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor kyang //
NK122(kho)001:902: bdun du nges par snang ba ste //
NK122(kho)001:903: dbang po mchog gi tha ma ni //
NK122(kho)001:904: lta sgom spyod pa ched 'dzin can //
NK122(kho)001:905: thabs dang shes rab sgor zhugs pas //
NK122(kho)001:906: smin grol thabs kyi bye brag kun //
NK122(kho)001:907: kun kyang thabs dang shes rab 'jug /
NK122(kho)001:910: ye nas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK122(kho)001:911: chen po lnga nyid bder gshegs lnga //
NK122(kho)001:912: 'byung lnga dbyings phyug shes rab lnga //
NK122(kho)001:913: de dag dbyer med khyad par las //
NK122(kho)001:914: rtog tshogs sems dpa' sems ma ste //
NK122(kho)001:915: rtag chad mthar lta reg pa'i tshogs //
NK122(kho)001:916: khro bo khro mo'i ngang du gsal //
NK122(kho)001:917: thams cad rig pa'i cho 'phrul las //
NK122(kho)001:918: kun bzang rol pa 'gag pa med //
NK122(kho)001:919: de nyid dus na 'dus ma byas //
NK122(kho)001:920: ma skyes chos nyid bzang mo'i dbyings //
NK122(kho)001:921: ma skyes mi 'gag dbyer med pa //
NK122(kho)001:922: byang sems bde chen de bzhin nyid //
NK122(kho)001:923: rnal 'byor chen po'i lta ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:926: bskyed pa rnam bzhi rim gyis bskyed //
NK122(kho)001:927: cho 'phrul rnam bzhi phyag rgya bzhi //
NK122(kho)001:928: dus bzhi'i rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK122(kho)001:929: rig pa rang snang dkyil 'khor gnyis //
NK122(kho)001:930: chu dang chu bzhin dbyer med de //
NK122(kho)001:931: ma skyes chos nyid shes rab las //
NK122(kho)001:933: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa //
NK122(kho)001:934: rnal 'byor chen po'i bsam gtan yin //
NK122(kho)001:935: rnal 'byor chen po'i spyod pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:936: bsnyen sgrub bzhi dang phrin las bzhi //
NK122(kho)001:937: sbyor sgrol la sogs spyod pa'i chos //
NK122(kho)001:938: bdag dang gzhan don bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)001:939: thabs kyis zin te nyams su blang //
NK122(kho)001:940: des ni bdag gzhan grol bar 'gyur //
NK122(kho)001:941: rnal 'byor chen po'i dam tshig ni //
NK122(kho)001:942: byang chub sems sogs rtsa ba bzhi //
NK122(kho)001:943: spyad pa lnga dang mi spangs lnga //
NK122(kho)001:944: dang du blang dang bsgrub pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:945: shes par bya ba lnga sogs dang //
NK122(kho)001:946: thun mong thun mong ma yin pa'i //
NK122(kho)001:947: bye brag sna tshogs bcas pa rnams //
NK122(kho)001:948: 'das nyams med par nyams su blang //
NK122(kho)001:949: mi tshe gcig la mngon grub ste //
NK122(kho)001:950: rtsal mchog ldan pa'i skyes bu ni //
NK122(kho)001:951: lhag mar bcas pa'i lus nyid kyis //
NK122(kho)001:952: las dang nyon mongs kun bral nas //
NK122(kho)001:953: tshe la dbang sogs rig 'dzin thob //
NK122(kho)001:954: rig pa 'dzin pa'i tshe nyid kyis //
NK122(kho)001:955: skye 'chi med pa'i sa bzung nas //
NK122(kho)001:956: longs spyod rdzogs dang sprul pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:957: tshul gyis 'gro rnams rgyud sbyangs te //
NK122(kho)001:958: bder gshegs zhing rnams spyod byed cing //
NK122(kho)001:959: sems can sdug bsngal gnas las sgrol //
NK122(kho)001:960: rgyal tshogs nye ba'i sras gyur cing //
NK122(kho)001:961: byang chub sems dpa' kun gyi spun //
NK122(kho)001:962: 'jig rten kun gyi rje bor lhag /
NK122(kho)001:963: brgya phrag bcu drug tshun chad du //
NK122(kho)001:964: shes bya phra sgrib byang gyur nas //
NK122(kho)001:965: rnal 'byor rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i sa //
NK122(kho)001:966: sku lnga lhun gyis grub par 'gyur //
NK122(kho)001:967: lung las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK122(kho)001:968: tha ma bskyed pa gang snang ba //
NK122(kho)001:969: thabs dang shes rab rnam dag pas //
NK122(kho)001:970: brten pa lnga las sogs pa'i rdzas //
NK122(kho)001:971: rgyal ba lnga ru rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK122(kho)001:972: rnal 'byor rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i sa //
NK122(kho)001:973: zhes gsungs lung gis bgrod dang gsal //
NK122(kho)001:974: 'bring la rdzogs pa'i tshul snang ba //
NK122(kho)001:975: rnam grol rigs pa'i tan+t+ra ste //
NK122(kho)001:976: de yang ltos pa'i bye brag bdun //
NK122(kho)001:977: dbang po rab kyi 'bring gyur pa //
NK122(kho)001:978: dbyings dang ye shes 'jug pa'i sgo //
NK122(kho)001:979: rnal 'byor rdzogs pa'i lta ba ni //
NK122(kho)001:980: bla med sangs rgyas man chad nas //
NK122(kho)001:981: na raka dmyal khams yan chad du //
NK122(kho)001:982: snod bcud phra rags bem rig dang //
NK122(kho)001:983: dge sdig mtho dman bzang ngan rnams //
NK122(kho)001:984: bye brag rnam pa cir snang yang //
NK122(kho)001:985: ngo bo nyid kyis ma skyes pas //
NK122(kho)001:986: mi dmigs mi gnas spros dang bral //
NK122(kho)001:987: gzung dang mtshan ma'i dngos po med //
NK122(kho)001:988: ma skyes ma bcos sems kyi dbyings //
NK122(kho)001:989: de nyid 'gag pa med rtsal gyis //
NK122(kho)001:990: thams cad thams cad mi 'gags pa //
NK122(kho)001:991: ye shes rol pa'i rgyan du rdzogs //
NK122(kho)001:993: bzhi po rim gyis ma bskyed de //
NK122(kho)001:995: dwangs pa'i mtsho la gza' skar bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:996: rig pa rtsal gyi byin rlabs kyis //
NK122(kho)001:997: mi bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul du bsgom //
NK122(kho)001:998: rnam grol rig pa'i spyod pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:999: rnal 'byor che dang bye brag med //
NK122(kho)001:1000: brtul zhugs nyi shu rtsa gsum po //
NK122(kho)001:1001: lung las bshad pa de dag yin //
NK122(kho)001:1002: bsrung ba'i dam tshig 'di lta ste //
NK122(kho)001:1003: sum brgya drug cu mtha' yas te //
NK122(kho)001:1004: gong 'og bsrung ba'i bye brag rnams //
NK122(kho)001:1005: 'di yis mi bsrung gcig kyang med //
NK122(kho)001:1006: zla ba lo dang lo bcu gnyis //
NK122(kho)001:1007: bcu drug rgyun gyi khyad par gyis //
NK122(kho)001:1008: 'khor lo tshogs chen mngon gyur rim //
NK122(kho)001:1009: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin du //
NK122(kho)001:1010: mngon du gyur pa lam gyi yun //
NK122(kho)001:1011: deng nas ring por mi thogs par //
NK122(kho)001:1012: brdal ba chos nyid sa zhes sam //
NK122(kho)001:1013: kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i sar //
NK122(kho)001:1014: thogs med mngon gyur lhun gyis grub //
NK122(kho)001:1015: lung las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK122(kho)001:1016: mnyam pas mnyam pa'i don mthong nas //
NK122(kho)001:1017: mnyam rdzogs yul shes dbyings ye shes //
NK122(kho)001:1018: kun rig kun rdzogs kun tu snang //
NK122(kho)001:1019: thams cad brdal ba chos nyid sa //
NK122(kho)001:1020: zhes gsungs lung gis bgrod dang gsal //
NK122(kho)001:1021: theg pa kun gyi spyi dpal te //
NK122(kho)001:1022: shin tu rnal 'byor theg pa'i bla //
NK122(kho)001:1023: bya bral rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK122(kho)001:1024: rang byung ye shes lhun grub pas //
NK122(kho)001:1025: tha snyad bye brag ma mchis kyang //
NK122(kho)001:1026: 'og ma dag la ltos chos kyang //
NK122(kho)001:1027: 'jug sgo la sogs bdun du dbye //
NK122(kho)001:1028: sngon sbyangs skyes bu skal ldan can //
NK122(kho)001:1029: dbang po rab kyi yang rab ni //
NK122(kho)001:1030: 'di tshe gcig la mngon rdzogs nus //
NK122(kho)001:1031: 'jug pa'i rten gyi gang zag yin //
NK122(kho)001:1032: lung las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK122(kho)001:1033: gleng bral nyid la gnas pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:1034: rnal 'byor de ni skal ba bzang //
NK122(kho)001:1036: sngon sbyangs skyes bu skal ldan rnal 'byor don //
NK122(kho)001:1037: bla ma'i man ngag snyan khungs thugs brgyud cing //
NK122(kho)001:1038: dad can rgyal ba'i thugs dang 'dra rnams khyer //
NK122(kho)001:1040: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK122(kho)001:1041: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas shing //
NK122(kho)001:1042: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK122(kho)001:1044: zhes gsungs phyir na lung gis gsal //
NK122(kho)001:1045: theg pa'i yang rtser 'jug pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:1046: bla med sangs rgyas man chad nas //
NK122(kho)001:1047: mnar med dmyal ba yan chad du //
NK122(kho)001:1048: gnyis snang phyi nang chos 'di rnams //
NK122(kho)001:1049: thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs pas //
NK122(kho)001:1050: phyogs lhung bral ba 'jug sgo yin //
NK122(kho)001:1051: bya bral rdzogs pa'i lta ba ni //
NK122(kho)001:1052: chos kun ma 'dres yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK122(kho)001:1053: 'beb tshul brjod pa mtha' yas kyang //
NK122(kho)001:1054: skabs 'dir phyogs phran tsam zhig bzung //
NK122(kho)001:1055: 'dir ni sgrub pa'i gtan tshigs bzhi //
NK122(kho)001:1056: rang bzhin skye ba med pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:1057: kun bzang rol pa 'gag pa med //
NK122(kho)001:1058: mtshan nyid dbye ba med pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:1059: ngo bo rang grol gtan tshigs te //
NK122(kho)001:1060: gtan tshigs bzhi ru rgyal bas bshad //
NK122(kho)001:1061: rang bzhin skye med gtan tshigs ni //
NK122(kho)001:1063: dge sdig bzang ngan la sogs pa //
NK122(kho)001:1064: zhen brtags gnyis snang chos 'di rnams //
NK122(kho)001:1065: mthun snang cha la 'gag med par //
NK122(kho)001:1066: so so nyid nas chos nyid dang //
NK122(kho)001:1067: ma bcos ma byas gnyen po med //
NK122(kho)001:1068: bye brag tha snyad spyod yul bral //
NK122(kho)001:1069: mu mtha' med pas ye shes klong //
NK122(kho)001:1070: mtha' dbus med pas brdal ba che //
NK122(kho)001:1071: 'od bsdu med pas thams cad khyab //
NK122(kho)001:1072: de yi bla dwags bye brag ni //
NK122(kho)001:1073: chos nyid ma skyes chos kyi dbyings //
NK122(kho)001:1074: mu med khyab brdal chen po'i klong //
NK122(kho)001:1075: ci bzhin pa yi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK122(kho)001:1076: rnal ma don gyi kun gzhi dang //
NK122(kho)001:1077: shes rab pha rol phyin la sogs //
NK122(kho)001:1078: skye med bla dwags bsam mtha' yas //
NK122(kho)001:1079: thams cad thams cad der gcig kyang //
NK122(kho)001:1080: de la phyogs ris mi mnga' phyir //
NK122(kho)001:1081: rang bzhin skye med gtan tshigs brjod //
NK122(kho)001:1082: rol pa 'gag med gtan tshigs ni //
NK122(kho)001:1084: snod bcud bde sdug rgyu 'bras dang //
NK122(kho)001:1085: gnyis par snang ba'i chos 'di rnams //
NK122(kho)001:1086: so so rang rtsal 'gag med de //
NK122(kho)001:1087: brtag pa'i zhen blos brtags bzhin no //
NK122(kho)001:1088: gang yang spangs len 'gag med phyir //
NK122(kho)001:1089: kun bzang rol pa'i rgyun zhes bya //
NK122(kho)001:1090: 'gag pa med dang mthun snang dang //
NK122(kho)001:1091: lhun grub dkyil 'khor thams cad de //
NK122(kho)001:1092: theg pa kun gyis gzhal bya dang //
NK122(kho)001:1093: mu stegs log brtags 'khrul gzhi dang //
NK122(kho)001:1094: 'jig rten pa yi zhen phyogs rnams //
NK122(kho)001:1096: rtogs grol ma rtogs dus na 'ching //
NK122(kho)001:1097: log brtags shin tu 'ching bar gsungs //
NK122(kho)001:1098: the tshom lam yang yun ring ngo //
NK122(kho)001:1099: de la 'jig rten thun mong pa //
NK122(kho)001:1100: 'byung chen nus pa nyid brtags te //
NK122(kho)001:1101: zhen pas yul gyi 'ching ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:1102: rtag par lta bas dngos por 'dzin //
NK122(kho)001:1103: rang gi grub mtha' nyid du 'dod //
NK122(kho)001:1104: nyan thos rnams kyi rdul phran te //
NK122(kho)001:1105: the tshom gcod pas cung zad grol //
NK122(kho)001:1106: rang sangs rgyas kyi rdul phran dang //
NK122(kho)001:1107: phyi nang rten 'brel brtags pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:1109: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis ni //
NK122(kho)001:1110: la las 'khrul gzhi sems su smra //
NK122(kho)001:1111: la las chad gzhi stong par smra //
NK122(kho)001:1112: kun rdzob bden par ming brtags te //
NK122(kho)001:1113: mi bslu'i tshul gyis gzhan don spyod //
NK122(kho)001:1114: gsang sngags theg pas lha ru 'dod //
NK122(kho)001:1115: de yang bye brag rnam gnyis te //
NK122(kho)001:1116: la las dag pa lha ru 'dod //
NK122(kho)001:1117: la las de nyid lha ru 'dod //
NK122(kho)001:1118: bya bral lhun gyis grub pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:1119: rang bzhin cir yang ma yin la //
NK122(kho)001:1120: rol pa cir yang mi 'gag pas //
NK122(kho)001:1122: mtshan nyid dbyer med gtan tshigs ni //
NK122(kho)001:1123: chu nyid rlabs su shar ba'am //
NK122(kho)001:1124: lho sprin nyid na stong pa bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:1125: rol pa 'gag pa med dus na //
NK122(kho)001:1126: skye med dbyings las g.yos pa med //
NK122(kho)001:1128: don byed rgyu rkyen sna tshogs smin //
NK122(kho)001:1129: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK122(kho)001:1130: lung las kyang ni 'di skad du //
NK122(kho)001:1131: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges pas //
NK122(kho)001:1132: ci ltar bltas pa de ltar snang //
NK122(kho)001:1134: med pa'i rgyu las yongs gsal bas //
NK122(kho)001:1135: snang nyid rang bzhin sgyu ma 'dra //
NK122(kho)001:1137: ji ltar nam mkha'i sprin bzhin du //
NK122(kho)001:1138: sna tshogs rnam pa cir snang yang //
NK122(kho)001:1139: de dus rang bzhin nyams pa med //
NK122(kho)001:1140: de sogs sna tshogs lung gis gsal //
NK122(kho)001:1141: bden gnyis dbyer med ces kyang bya //
NK122(kho)001:1142: byang sems dbyer med ces kyang bya //
NK122(kho)001:1143: dbyer med lhun grub ces kyang bya //
NK122(kho)001:1144: zung 'jug chen po zhes kyang bya //
NK122(kho)001:1145: mnyam rdzogs chen po zhes kyang bya //
NK122(kho)001:1146: de sogs grub matha'i bre brag gis //
NK122(kho)001:1147: sna tshogs bla dwags bsam mtha' yas //
NK122(kho)001:1148: rig pa rang grol gtan tshigs ni //
NK122(kho)001:1149: gang zhig skyes bu skal ldan can //
NK122(kho)001:1150: ma nor dam pa'i gsung la brten //
NK122(kho)001:1151: shes rab gsum gyis rgyud sbyangs te //
NK122(kho)001:1152: rgyu rkyen drug la me ltar g.yo //
NK122(kho)001:1153: gtan tshigs gsum la blo gdal bas //
NK122(kho)001:1154: srid pa'i chos rnams rang sar grol //
NK122(kho)001:1155: nyon mongs sdug bsngal shugs kyis zhi //
NK122(kho)001:1156: rnam shes yul sems gnas su dag /
NK122(kho)001:1157: rang byung ye shes klong du shar //
NK122(kho)001:1158: snang stong gang la'ang rten 'cha' bral //
NK122(kho)001:1159: phyogs lhung bral ba'i lta ba 'char //
NK122(kho)001:1160: bya bral rdzogs pa'i bsam gtan ni //
NK122(kho)001:1161: rang byung ye shes bde chen gyi //
NK122(kho)001:1162: klong du rang blo bdal ba ni //
NK122(kho)001:1163: shes sgrub dmigs pa'i rten cha bral //
NK122(kho)001:1164: rang rig yul bral ye shes ni //
NK122(kho)001:1165: bsam gtan kun gyi ngo bor byung //
NK122(kho)001:1166: lung las kyang ni 'di skad gsungs //
NK122(kho)001:1167: snang ba med pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK122(kho)001:1168: ma btsal bzhag na sgom pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:1169: zhes sogs gsungs pas mngon du 'byin //
NK122(kho)001:1170: bya bral rdzogs pa'i spyod pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:1171: spyod yul rgyun gyi 'khor lo la //
NK122(kho)001:1172: bya spyod bral ba'i rig pa 'char //
NK122(kho)001:1173: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:1174: dug gsum dug lnga la sogs rnams //
NK122(kho)001:1175: 'gag med rang byung nyid du gsal //
NK122(kho)001:1176: spangs blang med pa'i spyod pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:1178: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshig gis //
NK122(kho)001:1179: chos dbyings dag pa'i ngo bor shar //
NK122(kho)001:1180: rgyan dang cha lugs ldan spyod yin //
NK122(kho)001:1181: bla med theg pa man chad nas //
NK122(kho)001:1182: 'jig rten bya spyod yan chad kun //
NK122(kho)001:1183: ched kyis dgag sgrub gang yang med //
NK122(kho)001:1184: rang byung ye shes nyid du gsal //
NK122(kho)001:1185: bsam gyis mi khyab spyod pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:1186: thog mtha' dus dang snod bcud rnams //
NK122(kho)001:1187: lhun grub rang byung ye shes kyi //
NK122(kho)001:1188: rtsal du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK122(kho)001:1189: bdag nyid chen po'i spyod pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:1190: spyod pa'i khyad par ci byung yang //
NK122(kho)001:1191: dgag sgrub ched 'dzin bral bas na //
NK122(kho)001:1192: spyod pa'i rgyal po byar med yin //
NK122(kho)001:1193: bya bral rdzogs pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK122(kho)001:1194: chos nyid ngang las 'da' nyams med //
NK122(kho)001:1195: rig pa ye shes 'da' nyams med //
NK122(kho)001:1197: spang blang med pa'i spyod pa yis //
NK122(kho)001:1198: bla med theg pa'i dam tshig dang //
NK122(kho)001:1199: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa dang //
NK122(kho)001:1200: sdom pa'i bye brag mtha' yas dang //
NK122(kho)001:1201: thun mong bya spyod thams cad kun //
NK122(kho)001:1202: ched du dgag pa gcig kyang med //
NK122(kho)001:1203: ched du 'dzin pa yang bral ba //
NK122(kho)001:1204: bla med theg pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK122(kho)001:1205: bla med theg pa'i 'grub yun ni //
NK122(kho)001:1206: chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK122(kho)001:1207: ngo bo'i dus zhes bshad pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:1208: gtan tshig gsum la blo gdal nas //
NK122(kho)001:1209: rig pa rang sar grol ba'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:1210: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi //
NK122(kho)001:1211: 'go bo zug pa yin pas na //
NK122(kho)001:1212: sa chen dang po nye bar non //
NK122(kho)001:1213: g.yo ba'i nyams zhes bya ba yin //
NK122(kho)001:1214: de nyid nyams su blang ba'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:1215: sa chen gnyis pa non pa ste //
NK122(kho)001:1216: thob pa'i nyams zhes grags pa yin //
NK122(kho)001:1217: ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i tshe //
NK122(kho)001:1218: phyogs bcur bzhugs shing dus bzhir gshegs //
NK122(kho)001:1219: bder gshegs ma lus thams cad dang //
NK122(kho)001:1220: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje ltar //
NK122(kho)001:1221: dbyer med brtan pa mthar phyin yin //
NK122(kho)001:1222: sa rnams kun gyi yang thog ste //
NK122(kho)001:1223: bgrod pa'i lam gyi tha ma non //
NK122(kho)001:1224: thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs pas //
NK122(kho)001:1225: rdzogs pa'i spyir chibs sa zhes bya //
NK122(kho)001:1226: thams cad mthar phyin 'bras bu'i mchog /
NK122(kho)001:1227: ngo bo rnam grangs nges tshig dang //
NK122(kho)001:1228: bye brag snang tshul bstan pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:1229: ngo bo sku gsum lhun grub yin //
NK122(kho)001:1230: rnam grangs sku gsung thugs yon tan //
NK122(kho)001:1231: phrin las re re'ang lnga lnga ste //
NK122(kho)001:1232: rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyi shu lnga //
NK122(kho)001:1233: bye brag rnam grangs bsam mi khyab //
NK122(kho)001:1234: mthar phyin don bcas ldog med pas //
NK122(kho)001:1235: sgrub pa kun gyi mchog yin phyir //
NK122(kho)001:1236: 'bras bu'i nges tshig rgyal bas gsungs //
NK122(kho)001:1237: bye brag theg pa'i thob tshul te //
NK122(kho)001:1238: phyogs gcig pa dang ma 'dres dang //
NK122(kho)001:1239: lhun grub ye shes rang 'char ba //
NK122(kho)001:1240: thob tshul yin te dbye ba med //
NK122(kho)001:1241: snang tshul nye bar bstan pa ni //
NK122(kho)001:1242: gnyis med ye shes rang byung ba //
NK122(kho)001:1243: de bzhin gshegs pa snang ba dang //
NK122(kho)001:1244: longs spyod mdzad pa rgya chen rnams //
NK122(kho)001:1245: rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs //
NK122(kho)001:1246: smin pa rnams kyi spyod yul yin //
NK122(kho)001:1247: 'gro drug mos pa bsam yas pas //
NK122(kho)001:1248: so so'i mthun snang bsam yas su //
NK122(kho)001:1249: dwangs pa'i mtsho la gza' skar bzhin //
NK122(kho)001:1250: 'char ba de dag sprul pa'i sku //
NK122(kho)001:1251: sku gsum snang tshul tha dad kyang //
NK122(kho)001:1252: blo gsal nyi 'od gcig pa ltar //
NK122(kho)001:1253: ngo bo nyid la dbye ba med //
NK122(kho)001:1254: des na ma rtogs log par rtog /
NK122(kho)001:1255: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK122(kho)001:1256: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba dang //
NK122(kho)001:1257: rang bzhin gsang ba'i don rnams ces //
NK122(kho)001:1258: rgyud las gsungs pa de ltar yin /
NK122(kho)001:1259: kun bzang la sogs rgyal ba rgya mtshos bstan pa dam chos rgya mtsho ji snyed rnams /
NK122(kho)001:1260: rgyal tshab rgyal sras smin pa rgya mtsho dgos 'brel tshul gyis dgongs dang rig pa rna brgyud pa //
NK122(kho)001:1261: rgyud gzhung rgya che rgya mtsho'i chu las ngang pas 'o ma'i bcud blangs ji bzhin du //
NK122(kho)001:1262: theg pa'i bye brag phyogs dang phyogs min nges sgrub 'di bsdus 'gro kun yongs la bsngo //
NK122(kho)001:1263: theg pa'i bye brag mtha' yas pa las mdo tsam
NK122(kho)001:1264: zhig bkod pa bla ma rin po che dam pa'i
NK122(kho)001:1265: zhal nas dris pa rdzogs so ////
NK122(kho)001:1266: ni gnas skabs re zhig bshad du ma mchis pa'o //
NK122(kho)001:1268: skyes chen yab sras rnam gsum gyis //
NK122(kho)001:1270: zhal gsungs yig bris mchan btab pa //
NK122(kho)001:1271: de don 'phags mchog drin chen gyis //
NK122(kho)001:1272: t+ai ka gsal byed byas na yang //
NK122(kho)001:1273: blo dman rnams kyis phig dka' bas //
NK122(kho)001:1274: de phyir bshad mchan 'di byas so //
NK122(kho)001:1275: don la nor 'khrul gyur srid na //
NK122(kho)001:1276: bshags te ma nor dge ba des //
NK122(kho)001:1278: mthar phyin sku lnga 'grub par shog /
NK122(kho)001:1279: mchan bu 'di ni tshul khrims snying rjes bskul ba'i ngor //
NK122(kho)001:1280: nam mkha' rgyal mtshan gyis pha yul 'bri zla ba sgang gi ri khrod du bris pa'o //
NK122(kho)001:1281: drin chen ga ga ke tu'i thugs rnam dag /
NK122(kho)001:1282: rgyud snying man ngag nying khu theg shan 'byed //
NK122(kho)001:1283: zhal gsung bshad mchan bsdus don rin chen phreng //
NK122(kho)001:1284: dngos dang ma 'ongs rnams kyi ched bkod do //
NK122(kho)001:1285: slob dpon chen po nam mkha' rgyal mtshan pa'i thugs
NK122(kho)001:1286: kyi dgongs pa zhal du phyungs pa'i mchan rang dang
NK122(kho)001:1287: sa gtsong blo gsal ba dang sems la 'dun pa
NK122(kho)001:1288: thob pa rnams kyi don du gsungs pa 'di /
NK122(kho)001:1289: 'khor gyi nang nas 'bangs kyi tha mar gyur pa
NK122(kho)001:1290: tshul seng gis yul 'bri zla ba sgang gi gnam
NK122(kho)001:1291: gzung dben gnas dga' ldan ri khrod du bris pa'o
NK122(kho)001:1292: // 'di bris dge ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK122(kho)001:1293: bdag rgyud smin cing gzhan rgyud grol bar shog /'dir smras pa /
NK122(kho)001:1295: thub bstan gangs kyi ri la gnas bcas te //
NK122(kho)001:1296: phul byung shes rab dam pa'i rtsal rdzogs nas //
NK122(kho)001:1297: 'jigs med spobs pa chen po'i seng ge'i sgras //
NK122(kho)001:1298: gsang chen smra ba'i dbang phyug bde gshegs nyid /
NK122(kho)001:1300: 1 / dri med gsung gi nyi ma'i 'od zer gyis //
NK122(kho)001:1301: 'gro blo'i rmongs pa'i mun pa rnam bsal nas //
NK122(kho)001:1302: blo gros pad+mo'i dpal kun rgyas byed pa'i //
NK122(kho)001:1303: bla med theg pa'i rnam bshad 'di rmad byung /
NK122(kho)001:1305: 2 / gnas lnga rig pa'i dbang phyug pan chen rjes //
NK122(kho)001:1306: skye srid gnyis par zlos pa'i sgyu 'phrul gar //
NK122(kho)001:1307: tshe dbang rig pa 'dzin pa'i rgya mtsho yis //
NK122(kho)001:1308: bstan la rnam par dkar ba'i blo gros kyis /
NK122(kho)001:1310: 3 / ma lus theg pa'i dbye bsdu ji snyed pa //
NK122(kho)001:1311: rgyal dang rgyal sras lam bzang spyi yi chings //
NK122(kho)001:1312: srid zhir snang ba'i dpal ster mtshungs bral ba //
NK122(kho)001:1313: lhag bsam dag pas spar du bsgrub pa las /
NK122(kho)001:1315: 4 / dri med dge ba ston zla ltar dkar bas //
NK122(kho)001:1316: lus can gdung ba'i mun pa mthar byas nas //
NK122(kho)001:1317: bshad sgrub kun+da dkar po'i dpal rgyas te //
NK122(kho)001:1318: dge legs snang ba chen pos khyab gyur cig 5 /
NK122(kho)001:1319: ces pa'ang sprul pa'i sku rin po che tshe dbang rig 'dzin rgya mtshos /
NK122(kho)001:1320: rje btsun shes rab seng ge'i gsung dri ma med
NK122(kho)001:1321: pa 'di nyid rgyal bstan rin po che gsal bar
NK122(kho)001:1322: byed pa'i rgyan du dgongs nas mkhan rin po che
NK122(kho)001:1323: pad+ma badz+ra pas kyang phyi mo zhu dag byed pa
NK122(kho)001:1324: sogs / 'bad pa du mas bsgrub cing mthar phyin skabs /
NK122(kho)001:1325: mkhan ming lung rtogs bstan pa'i nyin byed dpal bzang pos spar byang du spel ba /
NK122(kho)001:1326: 'dis kyang rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa rin po che yun ring du gnas pa'i rgyur gyur cig //
